						Gluskin Sheff & Assoc Cut Oracle (ORCL) Stake, Loomis Sayles & Company LP Has Boosted By $15.13 Million Its Sherwin Williams (SHW) Holding - Bibey Post								







 


















 

























































Trending Stock News
Penny Stock News
Market News
Stock News






Gluskin Sheff & Assoc Cut Oracle (ORCL) Stake, Loomis Sayles & Company LP Has Boosted By $15.13 Million Its Sherwin Williams (SHW) Holding


					
						July 24, 2017 - By Migdalia James

Loomis Sayles & Company LP increased Sherwin Williams (SHW) stake by 20.71% reported in 2016Q4 SEC filing. Loomis Sayles & Company LP acquired 56,464 shares as Sherwin Williams (SHW)’s stock rose 6.75%. The Loomis Sayles & Company LP holds 329,159 shares with $88.46 million value, up from 272,695 last quarter. Sherwin Williams now has $32.94B valuation. The stock rose 0.04% or $0.14 reaching $352.31 per share. About 133,044 shares traded. Sherwin-Williams Co (NYSE:SHW) has risen 15.27% since July 24, 2016 and is uptrending. It has underperformed by 1.43% the S&P500.







Gluskin Sheff & Assoc Inc decreased Oracle Corporation (ORCL) stake by 1.75% reported in 2016Q4 SEC filing. Gluskin Sheff & Assoc Inc sold 11,820 shares as Oracle Corporation (ORCL)’s stock rose 5.35%. The Gluskin Sheff & Assoc Inc holds 662,468 shares with $25.47M value, down from 674,288 last quarter. Oracle Corporation now has $208.13 billion valuation. The stock declined 0.31% or $0.16 reaching $50.64 per share. About 1.40M shares traded. Oracle Corporation (NYSE:ORCL) has risen 14.08% since July 24, 2016 and is uptrending. It has underperformed by 2.62% the S&P500.
Among 20 analysts covering Sherwin-Williams Company (NYSE:SHW), 14 have Buy rating, 0 Sell and 6 Hold. Therefore 70% are positive. Sherwin-Williams Company had 33 analyst reports since July 22, 2015 according to SRatingsIntel. The stock has “Positive” rating by Susquehanna on Monday, March 21. RBC Capital Markets maintained Sherwin-Williams Co (NYSE:SHW) rating on Wednesday, November 25. RBC Capital Markets has “Outperform” rating and $336 target. The stock has “Buy” rating by Longbow on Wednesday, March 16. The firm earned “Buy” rating on Friday, June 23 by Citigroup. On Monday, June 26 the stock rating was maintained by RBC Capital Markets with “Buy”. The stock of Sherwin-Williams Co (NYSE:SHW) earned “Buy” rating by CLSA on Friday, July 22. The firm earned “Outperform” rating on Friday, October 30 by RBC Capital Markets. The firm earned “Neutral” rating on Wednesday, September 23 by Longbow. The stock of Sherwin-Williams Co (NYSE:SHW) has “Neutral” rating given on Thursday, January 5 by Longbow. The company was upgraded on Tuesday, November 8 by Evercore.
Investors sentiment decreased to 0.95 in 2016 Q4. Its down 0.15, from 1.1 in 2016Q3. It turned negative, as 64 investors sold SHW shares while 237 reduced holdings. 86 funds opened positions while 200 raised stakes. 66.23 million shares or 0.25% less from 66.39 million shares in 2016Q3 were reported. The Massachusetts-based Reynders Mcveigh Mngmt Ltd Llc has invested 0.1% in Sherwin-Williams Co (NYSE:SHW). Wade G W And, Massachusetts-based fund reported 988 shares. Ledyard Bancorp holds 136 shares. 5,437 are held by Gateway Advisers Limited Liability Corporation. Aqr Lc stated it has 249,967 shares. Parallax Volatility Advisers LP holds 2,272 shares. Chevy Chase owns 67,597 shares. Mutual Of America Mngmt Llc holds 9,445 shares or 0.05% of its portfolio. Triangle Securities Wealth Mngmt holds 1,709 shares or 0.31% of its portfolio. Jane Street Gru Ltd Liability holds 2,999 shares or 0% of its portfolio. Gradient Limited Co owns 287 shares or 0.01% of their US portfolio. Stephens Ar reported 5,848 shares stake. 600,000 were accumulated by Hitchwood Capital Management L P. Skylands Ltd Company has 0.32% invested in Sherwin-Williams Co (NYSE:SHW) for 7,790 shares. Thompson Siegel Walmsley Ltd Liability Co reported 0% stake.
Since January 27, 2017, it had 0 buys, and 11 selling transactions for $48.08 million activity. Shares for $346,588 were sold by Mistysyn Allen J. Another trade for 5,470 shares valued at $1.84 million was sold by Baxter Joel D.. GILLIGAN THOMAS P had sold 6,350 shares worth $2.15 million on Tuesday, May 9. Shares for $3.52 million were sold by Davisson Robert J. Connor Christopher M sold 117,458 shares worth $35.80M. On Friday, February 17 Wells Robert J sold $1.35M worth of Sherwin-Williams Co (NYSE:SHW) or 4,353 shares. CRONIN JANE M. sold 939 shares worth $286,254.
